// ============================================================
// FLUX APPARITION — v4 "SW4 Character Fix + SW2 Push"
// Concept:
//   Motion (chorus) + Space (reverb) as one instrument
//
// K1 Motion   : Chorus movement rate
// K2 Presence : Dry / Wet
// K3 Bloom    : Reverb sustain / density
// K4 Shape    : Chorus depth / spread
// K5 Bond     : Chorus <-> Reverb relationship
// K6 Color    : Global voicing (split internally for chorus/reverb)
//
// SW1 Halo      : Enables 3rd chorus voice
// SW2 Bond Mode : Stronger series / interaction behavior
// SW3 Orbit     : Wider / larger / cinematic mode
// SW4 Character : Bright Plate <-> Dark Hall
//
// FS1 Tap  : Chorus on/off
// FS1 Hold : Chorus freeze
// FS2 Tap  : Reverb on/off
// FS2 Hold : Reverb freeze
//
// Platform:
//   Daisy Petal / DaisySP / 48kHz / Mono In / Mono Out
// ============================================================

